  "summary": "This proposal outlines a smart contract interface for upgrading/downgrading existing [ERC-20](./eip-20.md) smart contracts while maintaining user balances. The interface itself is an extension to the ERC-20 standard so that other smart contracts can continue to interact with the upgraded smart contract without changing anything other than the address.",
